{
  "//": "Committed RELATIVE run/debug configs (no machine paths). Under Stonecutter each loader x MC version is its OWN Gradle project with its OWN resolved classpath, so each config targets a distinct `projectName` (nerospace-\u003cloader\u003e-\u003cversion\u003e) and TRULY runs that version when selected. Open nerospace.code-workspace, run `gradlew eclipse` once (generates the per-node .classpath/.project), reload VS Code, then pick a config in Run \u0026 Debug. preLaunchTasks regenerate per-machine launch args / loom launch.cfg for that node. All paths are relative (${workspaceFolder}); nothing here is machine-specific.",
